configset  GLOBAL  advertise_subscribed = [VALUE]
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Default Value : yes
Data Type     : bool, choose from: 0 n no, 1 y yes
Category      : lists
Password Notes: Visible only with password. Set with global password. 
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

EXAMPLE:
configset GLOBAL advertise_subscribed = 1


$INCLUDE-config/advertise_subscribed

If this setting is turned off, the access_rules setting, and possibly
the noadvertise and advertise configuration settings, are examined to
determine if a list is visible.


See Also:
   help configset_access_rules
   help configset_advertise
   help configset_noadvertise
   help lists

$INCLUDE-help/foot
